  {
    "title": "Lore",
    "depth": 1,
    "paragraphs": [
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "Amidst the misty mountains within the northern reaches of the Land of Dawn, resides the ancient and mysterious race of Centaurs, half-man, half-horse creatures.",
            "links": [
              {
                "type": "internal",
                "page": "Land of Dawn"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": "The Centaurs guard a fountain that rests among the highest mountain peak."
          },
          {
            "text": "This fountain is said to give the gift of Immortality and Infinite wisdom."
          },
          {
            "text": "Dark forces have relentlessly tried to gain the power found within the waters of this fountain, but only to be time and time again be thwarted by the centaurs."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "However, as time went on, the centaurs became tired and attrition soon took hold."
          },
          {
            "text": "It was not until Hylos had arrived, where he threw his mastery of nature's wrath, he was able to crush and punish all the invaders of the fountain."
          },
          {
            "text": "He had become a legendary figure within the annals of the Land of Dawn."
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "templates": [
      {
        "template": "clr"
      }
    ]
